Package: libmeasurement-kit-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libmeasurement-kit0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Portable C++11 network measurement library
 MeasurementKit is a network measurement library written in C++11 that
 implements network censorship tests (e.g. several OONI tests), and network
 performance tests (e.g. NDT).

